The thief's ability to let his/her eyes adjust and see better in
the dark, as well as see others who are "hiding". Using this skill
will allow you to use other Thief skills on the otherwise invisible
target. You have a short period of time (approx 10 seconds) after
you Squint to take action against the invisible target. This is
a Glevel 4 skill.

Syntax: squint

